The minions flew with great swiftness, quickly disappearing from all
Atlantean sensors as they flew into the western skies. It's only Remus
that is able to see them as he flew after them! 

As the speeds and distances increased the surface the minions flew over
changed from the sparkling blue of oceans to land - mountians and
forests racing beneath them in a blurr. It was here that Remus was
loosing pace with them fired his laser blasts, and then perhaps to his
surprise the entire host of sweeps, including Cyclonus and Scourge 
slowed and seemed to come to a stop swirling around the top of a
mountian. Almost as if waiting for Remus ....
